{"tid":2140751,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"美國 10 年內將製造無法破解的「量子網路」，但為何超怕「中繼器」做不出來？","createTime":"2020-08-05T08:04:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T14:59:24.000Z","uid":22675,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"909ee21ae2d7bdf3ad204c75484fad4afda1f9e9","tid":2140751,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T08:04:10.000Z","msg":"想像一個近乎無法破解、訊息儲存量高出傳統網路數倍的傳輸系統，這個技術將在 10 年內正式落實至美國在地網路中。美國能源局（Department of Energy, DOE）於上週四 發布藍圖 ，表示將利用量子運算的特性打造網路，「量子傳輸最棒的特性之一在於，訊息在兩地之前傳遞時，幾乎不可能遭竊取或竄改」。<br />\n<br />\n美國能源局早有動作，據外媒《Science Alert》指出，DOE 於今年 2 月已攜手美國芝加哥大學，於芝加哥郊區建立長達 83 公里的量子迴圈（Quantum Loop），長度相當於台北至新竹。此量子網路更創下國內有史以來最大的陸地量子網路。<br />\n<br />\n為什麼「量子傳輸」難以破解？<br />\n<br />\n量子運算並非使用傳統 1、0 位元運算，而是使用一種可以同時是 1 與 0 的量子位元（Qubits）。量子位元具備兩種特性，其一是位元只有在檢驗當下才會顯示是 1 或是 0，好比接住拋在空中的硬幣，唯有打開手掌才會知道是正面還是反面。其二則叫態疊加原理（Superposition），概念十分簡單。假設左右手都有著未知正反面的硬幣，若你打開左手檢視發現是正面，則 Superposition 將無視右手未知狀況，使連動的右手硬幣變成反面。<br />\n<br />\n透過量子位元的特性，當有駭客想竊取傳輸中的訊息，資訊很容易受影響導致壞損（funtion collapse）並且顯示出此訊息已遭暗中操作，使有心人士做事無法不露痕跡。再者，量子位元因為同時可以是 1 和 0，相比傳統 Bits 的資料承載力與密度高出許多。<br />\n<br />\n「量子傳輸」落地挑戰為何？<br />\n<br />\n時下資料傳輸皆使用光纖網路，利用光子乘載訊息在全世界到處來回。而由於光纖網路纖維的品質或耗損，光子容易消失不見，也就是所謂的訊號不良。中繼器（Repeater）就是偵測微弱訊號、接受並且強化後再次傳遞出去的儀器，透過中繼器便可維持網路品質不斷訊。不過量子位元無法用同一種方式處理，「你很難再接觸量子位元時不影響到它」芝加哥大學的研究人員 Awschalom 指出 ，沒有中繼器的情況下，量子位元最高只能傳遞約 160 公里的距離，對於如美國地區的全國性網路來說實在太短了。<br />\n<br />\n但事情還沒這麼簡單，要做到與傳統網路一樣能透過中繼器強化訊號，量子傳輸也需要打造「量子中繼器」，而此技術難到目前並沒有人做一個可以真正落地的產品過。<br />\n<br />\n量子運算擁有打破傳統產業運作模式的潛能，不談民間消費市場的使用，光是在科技研究、國防軍事上就能帶來難以想像的突破。而美國為了維持創新與科技大國，勢必得搶在全世界前跨出實驗的第一步。"},{"pid":"9290285b42497bcc8a5d9a538930cfdc3bbb4596","tid":2140751,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T08:04:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://buzzorange.com/techorange/2020/08/03/doe-quantum-internet/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuzzorange.com%2Ftechorange%2F2020%2F08%2F03%2Fdoe-quantum-internet%2F&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7Zearc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=101d2ef8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://buzzorange.com/techorange/2020/08/03/doe-quantum-internet/</a>"},{"pid":"b01967270d28f24450aa7bbfbdc88fd868657a80","tid":2140751,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T08:52:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2553483be296844f5af8992e80a25a1a67e4d1b6","tid":2140751,"uid":70487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T08:53:11.000Z","msg":"Gundam 00"},{"pid":"e83a4280f5ba04a5f5712dd3b54c2a0c79420500","tid":2140751,"uid":171506,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T08:56:03.000Z","msg":"唔知講乜"},{"pid":"1d3477881ab83b646b36ac3698a987ab581da1b7","tid":2140751,"uid":243677,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T08:59:07.000Z","msg":"睇唔明 但好似好勁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba7d3ea1dbd7ce9d1a74e47843772718d2aec304","tid":2140751,"uid":51006,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:00:46.000Z","msg":"entanglement 下話"},{"pid":"59d46ce615d323c1aa3ca3f6d81ad73697396170","tid":2140751,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:01:55.000Z","msg":"做到機構內資料密不透風已經差好遠  冇必要用黎做全國性網路"},{"pid":"e649b74118b35b31445b8ed8a886851442d34c6f","tid":2140751,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:04:26.000Z","msg":"content farm?"},{"pid":"ede04fcc370ce9b43ee58cfe541e56f885db0c1b","tid":2140751,"uid":15564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d3477881ab83b646b36ac3698a987ab581da1b7","tid":2140751,"uid":243677,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T08:59:07.000Z","msg":"睇唔明 但好似好勁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:08:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/薛定谔猫\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E8%96%9B%E5%AE%9A%E8%B0%94%E7%8C%AB&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7Zearc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=c8f47fab\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/薛定谔猫</a>"},{"pid":"192b0c5b9595dde7ce56daafa06e257d0fa4acf9","tid":2140751,"uid":36861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e649b74118b35b31445b8ed8a886851442d34c6f","tid":2140751,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:04:26.000Z","msg":"content farm?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:09:13.000Z","msg":"NO"},{"pid":"1f1a500ede2875a709900aba14622234f1af93ef","tid":2140751,"uid":261388,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:09:44.000Z","msg":"組係用一對相連粒子，異空間傳送MESSAGE ，改變A粒子，B粒子就會同樣改變， 無視空間同距離，第時如果有星際旅行可以無視距離即時通訊，甚至SET UP 一個交通中心，即時傳送物件同人"},{"pid":"9044493afd72a332c2e98258d704a7ba71d740ec","tid":2140751,"uid":97518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:13:40.000Z","msg":"對話果時係咪要裸體"},{"pid":"da8c593391fb108e2a42591c3a8e4d4395d7a10f","tid":2140751,"uid":36861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e649b74118b35b31445b8ed8a886851442d34c6f","tid":2140751,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:04:26.000Z","msg":"content farm?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:13:59.000Z","msg":"google 前年已經做産左53bit 量子電腦, 佢呢份野係話量子電腦用宜家既中繼器係中繼唔到,呢個世界係無量子中繼器呢樣野, 所以個limitation係個data只能最遠射到160km, 無得再遠, 唔實用。<br />\n<br />\n佢話美國要軍事化, 就一定要設計量子中繼器。(我覺得設計唔到出黎..神仙咩..<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"255c4214f56655e31f11adaf232cb5e845298954","tid":2140751,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:14:15.000Z","msg":"雖然我不知道你在說什麼<br />\n但聽起來好像很厲害<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9f4781245ddf5bccee93ba9c3e73d581dce70b","tid":2140751,"uid":361643,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e83a4280f5ba04a5f5712dd3b54c2a0c79420500","tid":2140751,"uid":171506,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T08:56:03.000Z","msg":"唔知講乜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:14:17.000Z","msg":"量子定理下 你一觀察佢就會有第二個結果出左黎 <br />\n篇野講緊就係 量子傳輸安全係因為黑客一hack 個data 就會冇左 所以做到100%安全<br />\n<br />\n但問題係因為你一睇佢 佢就會消失 但你又需要去確保佢唔會訊號不良 所以你要一樣野去加強番個訊號 但你一加強個訊號粒量子就會消失 <br />\n<br />\n所以成篇野就係講緊 美國10年內有能力實現短途量子傳輸 但長途傳輸技術就仲未克服到"},{"pid":"d3cadd02c1a9e502a21a19325c10e124e9ad413b","tid":2140751,"uid":36861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9044493afd72a332c2e98258d704a7ba71d740ec","tid":2140751,"uid":97518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:13:40.000Z","msg":"對話果時係咪要裸體"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:14:33.000Z","msg":"唔使呀...你打電話使唔使婐體呀"},{"pid":"2f7c8c2ae3a92dc58c237f270567a576a9584958","tid":2140751,"uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:31:55.000Z","msg":"量子領域，蟻俠同黃蜂女準備好未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce82985b7cfecac99b9c3893c68ded0f6968c468","tid":2140751,"uid":97518,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d3cadd02c1a9e502a21a19325c10e124e9ad413b","tid":2140751,"uid":36861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9044493afd72a332c2e98258d704a7ba71d740ec","tid":2140751,"uid":97518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:13:40.000Z","msg":"對話果時係咪要裸體"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:14:33.000Z","msg":"唔使呀...你打電話使唔使婐體呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:32:37.000Z","msg":"好明顯你唔睇高達"},{"pid":"02dffb428e4c3fdb33112575c8c71bc724eae8c4","tid":2140751,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:55:39.000Z","msg":"兩倍量子破一般量子"},{"pid":"c86a50a3017edc37951fef72749d6e68d23ae881","tid":2140751,"uid":31389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T10:09:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr